title: This thread has prolly been made at least 1000 times
body:
Why did I transfer to OCE and see no team builder or norms draft?
The hell?

replies.body: If you did some research before transferring, you would've known. Literally top of the boards is a sticky thread showing which queues we have and when [[link](http://img-9gag-fun.9cache.com/photo/a9P0B4W_460s_v1.jpg)].
